🔀 Shift Operators

| Operator | Name                 | Example    | Output |
| -------- | -------------------- | ---------- | ------ |
| `<<`     | Left Shift           | `5 << 1`   | `10`   |
| `>>`     | Signed Right Shift   | `10 >> 1`  | `5`    |
| `>>>`    | Unsigned Right Shift | `10 >>> 1` | `5`    |
